  "title": "Admin Assistant (Redhill)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Admin Assistant</strong></p><ul><li>Salary:  $2000 -$2200</li><li>Mon – Friday: 8.45am to 5.30pm, Alt Sat: 8.45am to 12.45pm</li><li>Location: Redhill (near to MRT Station) </li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities </strong></p><ul><li>Manage and respond to general and administrative email accounts; attend to sales, customer, and general inquiries.</li><li>Attend to and follow up on customer hotline complaints; maintain up-to-date customer contracts and records.</li><li>Update records for sales, sandwich disposals, and petty cash.</li><li>Prepare and compile monthly reports and required forms for drivers.</li><li>Handle cash counting (notes and coins) and cash-related responsibilities.</li><li>Update maintenance records as provided by the Operations Manager and Technician.</li><li>Manage weekly checking of GPS systems for all company vehicles.</li><li>Conduct weekly vehicle inspections.</li><li>Perform other related administrative duties as assigned.</li></ul><p>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619<br />The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
